course_description.character:
1,215 km loop from Umeå across Scandinavian peninsula to Norwegian Sea fjords/Mo i Rana and back. 13 controls: Lycksele (122 km), Storuman, Mo i Rana (546 km), Arctic Circle Centre (643 km), Tjaktjaure (722 km), Åmsele (1084 km). Asphalt via river valleys/lakes/fjords; snow-capped climbs to 647 m; 158 km remote stage.

**Suffering Zones:**
- Early border climb (headwinds/cold);
- 158 km monotonous remote;
- Norwegian mountains (snow/rain/narrow frost-damaged roads);
- Arctic Circle push (722 km isolation).
